%script{src: '/root.js'}
%div.container
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-10.col-sm-offset-1
      %div.jumbotron#slidetron{style: 'padding: 28px; background-image: url(/glas.png); display: none;'}
        %div.container
          %div.row
            %div.col-md-6.col-sm-offset-3
              %img.text-center{src: '/optumm.png', style: '-webkit-transform:rotate(2deg); -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; width: 100%;'}
          %h4.text-center{style: "font: 400 25px/1.3 'Lobster Two', Helvetica, sans-serif;"}
            Fancy a Ride?
  %div.row{style: 'margin-left: -150px; margin-right: -150px; padding: 20px; padding-top: 40px; background-image: url(/fabric.png);'}
    %div.col-md-7
      %iframe{:src=>"https://www.mapbox.com/bites/00011/", :frameborder=>"no", :width=>"100%", :height=>"300"}
      %h5.text-center
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-camera
        Tell your journey's story with timelapse recording via smart-phone.
    %div.col-md-4.col-sm-offset-1
      %iframe{:src=>"//www.youtube.com/embed/mrNSAqiO0SY?autoplay=1&controls=0&showinfo=0&rel=0&hd=", width: '91%', height: '300', frameborder: "0"}
      %h5.text-center{style: 'margin-left: -50px;'}
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-hand-up
        %a{href: 'http://far.include.cat'}
          HTML5 Smart-Map
        , optimised for mobile browsers.
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-6.col-sm-offset-3
      %h3.text-center{style: "font: 400 30px/1.3 'Lobster Two', Helvetica, sans-serif;"}
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-map-marker
        Our aim is to improve your cycling experience.
      %h5.text-center
        First in Glasgow, then in the wider world!

  %hr
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-6
      %h4
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-link
        How can I help?
      Let us know what you'd like to see in our app, with this
      %a{ :href => "/poll", :title => "Help Us Out!"}
        quick questionnaire!
      %br
      We value your honest feedback, throughout the development process.
      %br
      See the results of your feedback visualised in
      %a{ :href => "/results", :title => "Thanks for Helping us out!"}
        pretty chart form.

    %div.col-md-6
      %h4
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-eye-open
        Looking for goodies to play with?
      An online smart-map for orientation when out-and-about is available
      %a{href: 'http://far.include.cat'}
        here.
      %br
      Find a quick route to important resources, including public toilets and bike-racks!

  %hr
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-6.col-sm-offset-3
      %h3.text-center{style: "font: 400 30px/1.3 'Lobster Two', Helvetica, sans-serif;"}
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-volume-off
        Don't just take our word for it!
      %h5.text-center
        We interrupted some good-looking members of the general public (while they were trying to visit a museum in peace), just to check that we are on the right track.
  %hr
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-3
      %img.text-center{src: '/photo4.png', width: '150px', style: 'box-shadow: 5px 5px 5px #888888; border-radius: 100px;'}
    %div.col-md-9
      %blockquote
        %p
          "I quite fancy cycling the canal route into town."
  %hr
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-3.col-sm-offset-1
      %img.text-center{src: '/photo3.png', width: '150px', style: 'box-shadow: 5px 5px 5px #888888; border-radius: 100px;'}
    %div.col-md-8
      %blockquote
        %p
          "I do like cycling"
  %hr
  %div.row
    %div.col-md-3
      %img.text-center{src: '/photo1.png', width: '150px', style: 'box-shadow: 5px 5px 5px #888888; border-radius: 100px;'}
    %div.col-md-9
      %blockquote
        %p
          "I've not stopped cycling."


